7 An Act relating to the Oklahoma Department of
Transportation; making appropriations; identifying
8 sources of funds; stating purposes; providing an
effective date; and declaring an emergency.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma
13 Department of Transportation from any monies not otherwise
14 appropriated from the Progressing Rural Economic Prosperity Fund of
15 the State Treasury created in Section 256 of Title 62 of the
16 Oklahoma Statutes, the sum of Three Million Five Hundred Thousand
17 Dollars ($3,500,000.00) for the purpose of improving transportation
18 infrastructure with heavy industrial traffic located east of State
19 Highway 99/U.S. Highway 377 and north of State Highway 62.
20 SECTION 2. There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma
21 Department of Transportation from any monies not otherwise
22 appropriated from the Progressing Rural Economic Prosperity Fund of
23 the State Treasury created in Section 256 of Title 62 of the
24 Oklahoma Statutes, the sum of Four Million Eight Hundred Thousand
ENGR. H. B. NO. 4048 Page 1

1 Doll ars ($4,800,000.00) for the purpose of improving transportation
2 infrastructure with heavy industrial traffic located south of U.S.
3 Highway 412 and west of State Highway 385.
4 SECTION 3. There is hereby appropriated to the Oklahoma
5 Department of Transportation from any monies not otherwise
6 appropriated from the Progressing Rural Economic Prosperity Fund of
7 the State Treasury created in Section 256 of Title 62 of the
8 Oklahoma Statutes, the sum of Four Million Seven Hundred Thousand
9 Dollars ($4,700,000.00) for the purpose of improving transportation
10 infrastructure that serves as a main route for emergency services
11 located north of the Northwest Expressway/State Highway 3 and west
12 of State Highway 74.
13 SECTION 4. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
14 SECTION 5. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
15 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
16 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
17 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
